QuestionText: Given $X=\{a,b,c,d,f\}, T=\{\phi, X, \{a\}, \{a,b\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{a,b,c,d\}, \{a,b,f\}\}$ Find all the nbds of the point \\(i)$f$\\(ii)$c$
Find the interior, exterior, boundary for $A=\{b,c,d\}$ on the topology $X=\{a,b,c,d,f\}, T=\{\phi, X, \{a\}, \{c,d\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{b,c,d,f\}\}$.
Find the interior, exterior, boundary for $B=\{a,b,c\}$ on the topology $X=\{a,b,c,d,f\}, T=\{\phi, X, \{a\}, \{a,b\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{a,b,c,d\},\{a,b,f\}\}$.
Let $A=\{a,b,c\}$ and $X=\{a,b,c,d,f\}, T=\{\phi, X, \{a\}, \{c,d\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{b,c,d,f\}\}$ be a TS. Find $A'$ and $\bar{A}$.
Find the relative topology $T_A$ for $A=\{a,b,f\}$ on the topology $X=\{a,b,c,d,f\}, T=\{\phi, X, \{a\}, \{c,d\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{b,c,d,f\}\}$.
